## MailApi

### Place Mail Order
## Place Mail Order
POST https://my.interserver.net/apiv2/mail/order
Accept: application/json
Cookie: sessionid={{cookieKey}}
X-API-KEY: {{apiKey}}
sessionid: {{apiKey}}

### Create Deny Rule
## Create Deny Rule
POST https://my.interserver.net/apiv2/mail/{{id}}/rules
Content-Type: application/json
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Accept: application/json
Cookie: sessionid={{cookieKey}}
X-API-KEY: {{apiKey}}
sessionid: {{apiKey}}

{
  "user" : "mb20682",
  "type" : "email",
  "data" : "domeinwo@server.guesshost.net"
}


### Create Mail Alert
## Create Mail Alert
POST https://my.interserver.net/apiv2/mail/{{id}}/alerts
Content-Type: application/json
Content-Type: multipart/form-data
Accept: application/json
Cookie: sessionid={{cookieKey}}
X-API-KEY: {{apiKey}}
sessionid: {{apiKey}}

{
 "type": "<string>",
 "value": "<string>",
 "to": "<string>",
 "enabled": "<string>"
}


### Delete Mail Alert
## Delete Mail Alert
DELETE https://my.interserver.net/apiv2/mail/{{id}}/alerts?alertId={{alertId}}
Accept: application/json
Cookie: sessionid={{cookieKey}}
X-API-KEY: {{apiKey}}
sessionid: {{apiKey}}

### Delete Deny Rule
## Delete Deny Rule
DELETE https://my.interserver.net/apiv2/mail/{{id}}/rules/{{rule}}
